div.p:
Therefore farre bee it from any Christian Soule to account these men damned, as the Romanists doe, onely

for not being subiect to the Bishop of Rome,
      Bonif. 8. in extrar. de major. & obedi. cap. unam sanctam, &c. according to their Tenet: That every Soule must of necessity of Salvation be subject to the Bishop of Rome.
